  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the cutoff point for IVC collapsibility index (by
      Bedside Ultrasonographic technique) for cases in hypovolemic hemorrhagic shock with CVP
      measures less than 8 cmH2o.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
